casebody.data:
Diane L. RHODES-LYONS, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 13-8630. Supreme Court of the United States March 24, 2014.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied. Petitioner allowed until April 14, 2014, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule *157538(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.
